1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:03,940
(Episode 129)

2
00:00:15,650 --> 00:00:16,960
It's okay. Sit down.

3
00:00:18,790 --> 00:00:20,360
CEO Chae, why...

4
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:22,960
Why am I here?

5
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,330
I called you because I need you.

6
00:00:25,530 --> 00:00:27,630
I need your help, Jin Hong Ju.

7
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:28,970
What?

8
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:32,700
You need my help?

9
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:35,010
How am I supposed to help you?

10
00:00:35,310 --> 00:00:38,710
If the Chairman finds out,
my mom and I will be kicked out.

11
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:40,780
Before Chairman Ma kicks you out,

12
00:00:41,150 --> 00:00:43,010
I'm planning on taking him down myself.

13
00:00:43,650 --> 00:00:46,820
- What?
- You have no choice but to be on my side.

14
00:00:47,850 --> 00:00:51,190
But if the Chairman faints,

15
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:54,490
my mom and I are so powerless.

16
00:00:54,490 --> 00:00:56,060
Since when were you
such a devoted daughter?

17
00:00:57,030 --> 00:00:59,100
If Oh Jang Mi isn't
by Kang Baek Ho's side,

18
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,730
you can have Kang Baek Ho.

19
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:05,370
- I guess that's true, but...
- If you help me,

20
00:01:05,940 --> 00:01:07,870
I'll take care of Oh Jang Mi for you too.

21
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:11,540
I can deal with her and Chairman Ma
at the same time.

22
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:15,850
But if that happens,
will Baek Ho just stand by and do nothing?

23
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,980
I don't think he'll just sit back.

24
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:20,620
Bingo. That's exactly it, Jin Hong Ju.

25
00:01:21,090 --> 00:01:23,460
You don't have to worry about that.

26
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:27,990
Kang Baek Ho is Choi Ha Joon,
Dream Group's majority shareholder.

27
00:01:28,890 --> 00:01:32,700
But what if Chairman Ma tried to kill
Kang Baek Ho and his grandfather?

28
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:36,630
- What?
- There's no time to explain in detail.

29
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:38,200
Hurry up and decide.

30
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:39,970
Are you going to help me or not?

31
00:01:40,810 --> 00:01:42,370
Otherwise, you're my enemy.

32
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:45,110
Now that you've heard my entire plan,

33
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,680
you don't really have a choice, do you?

34
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:55,950
I'll help you.

35
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:58,390
But if I do,

36
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:02,530
will you really get Oh Jang Mi
away from Baek Ho?

37
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:04,460
Yes, I promise.

38
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:09,070
All right, now listen carefully.

39
00:02:09,570 --> 00:02:11,000
Here's what you have to do...

40
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:15,910
Oh my, sweetie.

41
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:18,040
What's the occasion?
It's so thoughtful of you...

42
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,740
to tell me to go see a musical.

43
00:02:19,810 --> 00:02:23,280
Don't worry about the house.
Just go out and have fun.

44
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,720
But today,

45
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:27,350
Geum Soon is on vacation
and comes back tomorrow,

46
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:30,360
and Suk Hee has
her granddaughter's kindergarten recital.

47
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,160
The Chairman is sick,

48
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:35,760
and I don't feel right
about leaving the house empty.

49
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:38,200
It's fine, I'll be here.

50
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:40,630
I took the day off,
so I'll be home all day.

51
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,330
Go on, Mom. Get some fresh air.

52
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,100
Well, thank you, sweetie.

53
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:51,180
I'm sorry, Mom.
I'm going to betray the Chairman.

54
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:55,580
This is also part of your project
to make Choi Ha Joon your son-in-law.

55
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:12,900
It's me.

56
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:14,770
Check the CCTV.

57
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:15,830
It's off, right?

58
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,800
Yes, it's off.

59
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:19,240
Then I'll turn it back on.

60
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,310
Yes, it's back on.

61
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,380
Good. And Chairman Ma?

62
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:29,150
He's resting in his room now.

63
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:32,050
Got it. I'll be there in 15 minutes.

64
00:03:32,580 --> 00:03:33,890
You set things up quickly...

65
00:03:33,890 --> 00:03:35,550
and then go to the hotel
and deal with Oh Jang Mi.

66
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:36,890
You can't make any mistakes.

67
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,090
We have to stick to the schedule.

68
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:40,220
Okay.

69
00:03:40,490 --> 00:03:42,030
So I just need to take
the pills you gave me...

70
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,300
and secretly put them
in Oh Jang Mi's bag, right?

71
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:46,600
Look carefully for any CCTV cameras
at the office.

72
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:49,370
And be careful not to leave
your fingerprints on the pill case.

73
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:50,400
Yes, I understand.

74
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,700
I'll get it set up and leave right away.

75
00:04:17,930 --> 00:04:21,830
(General Manager Ma Seo Rin)

76
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,150
General Manager Ma.

77
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:39,750
My mom had to go out,
and she called on her way.

78
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,650
She asked me to stay with the Chairman
since he's home alone.

79
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:43,960
Really?

80
00:04:47,330 --> 00:04:48,560
Secretary Kim, it's me.

81
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,530
Get over here now.

82
00:04:51,530 --> 00:04:54,200
We have to find Chae Hwa Young
and her cronies.

83
00:04:55,330 --> 00:04:56,330
What?

84
00:04:57,300 --> 00:04:59,370
What do you mean
you haven't found any trace of them yet?

85
00:05:00,770 --> 00:05:03,540
What about a hideout or something?

86
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:05,140
That too...

87
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:10,820
Hey! What do you think you're doing?

88
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,490
(My battery is low. I'll call you later.)

89
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,620
Hey, you witch.

90
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:19,190
Give that to me, now!

91
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:25,260
- It's been a while, Father.
- You...

92
00:05:25,530 --> 00:05:28,630
You have a lot of nerve coming here.

93
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:31,670
How dare you waltz into my house?

94
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:35,840
You clearly don't understand
the situation, do you?

95
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:38,110
Oh, I understand it perfectly.

96
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:42,080
I'm talking about
how you cunningly played me...

97
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,450
by turning Manager Lee and me
against each other.

98
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:47,950
Shut up!
You should be begging for your life.

99
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,190
Hey, you witch...

100
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:56,390
How dare you cause a scene, you old man?

101
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:58,560
- What did you say?
- You should just quietly leave in peace.

102
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,440
You venomous snake.

103
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:08,510
Do you think you can get away with this?

104
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:12,540
Did you forget there is CCTV
all over this house?

105
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:13,880
CCTV?

106
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:16,680
Don't you know I control them?

107
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:20,020
I can turn them on and off
with an app on my phone.

108
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:23,320
Unfortunately,
they aren't recording right now.

109
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,390
What a shame.

110
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:28,560
So what is it that you want?

111
00:06:29,990 --> 00:06:31,000
Money?

112
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,560
Or...

113
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,730
do you want to be reinstated as CEO?

114
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:37,700
No.

115
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,440
I want...

116
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,470
your life, Ma Dae Chang.

117
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:45,080
- What?
- Because today is the day you die.

118
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:49,010
- So state your last words.
- What? What did you just say?

119
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:53,120
It's starting to take effect.

120
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:56,050
You took your daily medication today,
didn't you?

121
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:59,520
It's fatal for you.

122
00:07:01,590 --> 00:07:02,590
What?

123
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:08,530
Chairman.

124
00:07:09,470 --> 00:07:12,000
If you take this medicine,
you'll feel much better.

125
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:16,410
This is the same medicine
I always take, right?

126
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,540
Of course.

127
00:07:19,610 --> 00:07:22,280
Then, did you...

128
00:07:22,850 --> 00:07:25,820
bribe Dr. Kim?

129
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,550
You wretched...

130
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:35,790
That's right. Who else would it be?

131
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:38,360
The medicine you've been taking...

132
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:40,800
is a powerful diuretic...

133
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,270
that looks just like
your blood pressure pills.

134
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,570
The effects have built up,

135
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:48,770
and it's having an explosive reaction
with the medication you took today.

136
00:07:49,910 --> 00:07:52,480
Do I have to explain everything so nicely
for you?

137
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:57,550
You demonic witch.

138
00:07:58,220 --> 00:08:01,550
Since this is the end of the road for you,
I'll tell you what this is.

139
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:05,660
Your granddaughter, Oh Jang Mi,
will be here soon.

140
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,360
And this...

141
00:08:09,730 --> 00:08:13,800
will be the evidence
that your granddaughter tried to kill you.

142
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,700
You murderous witch.

143
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,600
You...

144
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,180
(Stock Transfer Agreement)

145
00:08:28,250 --> 00:08:30,010
(A: Ma Dae Chang, B: Ma Seo Rin)

146
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:41,790
You've clung so tenaciously to life.

147
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:45,960
Now, let me be the one to sever it.

148
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:56,440
(Staffing Services, Housekeeper)

149
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,520
Yes, Manager Lee.

150
00:09:09,090 --> 00:09:10,520
I've taken care of Chairman Ma.

151
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,420
You put the tracker
on Oh Jang Mi's car, right?

152
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,090
When did she leave?

153
00:09:16,490 --> 00:09:19,230
Got it. I'll get things started now.

154
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,170
(389 Namseon-ro, Hangang-gu, Seoul)

155
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:26,300
Alright, Oh Jang Mi.

156
00:09:26,970 --> 00:09:28,610
Look at you, heading right on home.

157
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,550
Is this the police station?

158
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,320
This is Chae Hwa Young,
the CEO of Dream Hotel.

159
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:43,020
My CCTV alarm just went off,
and I think someone broke into my house.

160
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,990
Please come quickly. Hurry.

161
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:49,690
Yes. I'm looking at the CCTV footage
from the main gate now.

162
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,560
It's Ma Seo Rin. She's my daughter.

163
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:56,100
No. Lately,
because of some issues with her shares,

164
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,800
she's been constantly threatening
her grandfather.

165
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,640
She even caused her grandfather
to collapse.

166
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:05,380
I'm scared of what she might do this time.

167
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:07,410
Please come quickly. Hurry.

168
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,610
I'll head there right away too.

169
00:10:22,430 --> 00:10:25,130
Grandfather. Are you in the study?

170
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:31,540
Yes, perfect timing.

171
00:10:32,370 --> 00:10:34,940
Now it's time to hammer it home
for the police, isn't it?

172
00:10:36,370 --> 00:10:40,040
You're the ones who started
with the AI deepfake voice manipulation,

173
00:10:40,810 --> 00:10:42,680
so I'm just giving you a taste
of your own medicine.

174
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,180
Anyone home?

175
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:57,560
- Just stamp it already.
- How dare you!

176
00:10:58,130 --> 00:11:00,000
I treated you like my own granddaughter!

177
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,170
So just hand over the shares!

178
00:11:03,070 --> 00:11:04,340
Did you hear them fighting?

179
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:06,200
I think something's already happened.

180
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,910
I have to call 911.

181
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:17,850
Let go of him. Step away from the victim.

182
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:21,420
You're police officers, right?

183
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:24,120
Please call 911 for my grandfather.
Please?

184
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:31,260
- Why are you doing this?
- Ma Seo Rin,

185
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:33,230
you're under arrest...

186
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:34,670
for the attempted murder
of a lineal ascendant.

187
00:11:35,170 --> 00:11:39,470
You have the right to an attorney
and the right to remain silent.

188
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:42,840
Anything you say can be used against you
in a court of law.

189
00:11:43,110 --> 00:11:47,750
What? No. It wasn't me.

190
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:57,320
I made it here,

191
00:11:58,020 --> 00:11:59,720
but what am I supposed to ask
the Chairman to confirm?

192
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:04,630
But if the Chairman was lying,

193
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,560
what do I do?

194
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:18,210
Detective.

195
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:21,980
- I said it wasn't me.
- Jang Mi.

196
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,950
- What's going on?
- Baek Ho.

197
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:29,390
Grandfather collapsed.
We need to call 911.

198
00:12:29,450 --> 00:12:30,450
What should I do?

199
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,060
I'm a lawyer
with the Dream Group legal team.

200
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:34,860
- What's going on here?
- It's an attempted murder case.

201
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:37,330
- She was caught in the act.
- That's impossible.

202
00:12:37,330 --> 00:12:39,660
- Put her in the car.
- Baek Ho.

203
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:41,100
- Jang Mi.
- Baek Ho.

204
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,440
- There's been a mistake.
- Baek Ho.

205
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,610
Baek Ho.

206
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:49,870
Jang Mi.

207
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,580
I'm telling you there's been a mistake.

208
00:12:53,010 --> 00:12:54,480
- Jang Mi.
- Wait.

209
00:12:54,810 --> 00:12:55,980
Everything will be okay.

210
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:59,620
- Baek Ho.
- Jang Mi.

211
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,150
Jang Mi.

212
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:07,930
(Trustworthy Police, Safe Nation)

213
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:15,670
What is your name
and Resident Registration Number?

214
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,740
What about my grandfather?

215
00:13:18,370 --> 00:13:19,870
Is he okay?

216
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,740
The family will take care of that.

217
00:13:23,970 --> 00:13:27,010
Quickly state your name
and Resident Registration Number.

218
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:29,680
It's Oh Jang Mi.

219
00:13:30,210 --> 00:13:33,650
And my number is 961104-20431193.

220
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:36,850
(Identity Check: Oh Jang Mi, Deceased)

221
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:38,220
Oh Jang Mi?

222
00:13:38,690 --> 00:13:40,660
The records say this person is deceased.

223
00:13:40,930 --> 00:13:42,190
The fingerprints match Oh Jang Mi too.

224
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:45,630
What's going on?
The report was filed under Ma Seo Rin.

225
00:13:46,130 --> 00:13:48,200
Who reported me?

226
00:13:49,330 --> 00:13:50,530
Was it Chae Hwa Young?

227
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:53,070
That's none of your business.
Tell me the truth.

228
00:13:53,140 --> 00:13:54,640
You're facing serious felony charges.

229
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:57,910
If Chairman Ma is your grandfather,
that's attempted patricide.

230
00:13:57,980 --> 00:14:00,510
And using a stolen identity
will only make things worse.

231
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:01,950
Attempted murder?

232
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:04,920
When I got there,
my grandfather was already on the floor.

233
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:07,790
Why would I hurt my grandfather?
That's ridiculous.

234
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:10,620
We found your fingerprints
on the bloody golf club.

235
00:14:11,090 --> 00:14:13,590
- We have solid evidence.
- No, that's not true.

236
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:16,230
I only touched it
because it had blood on it,

237
00:14:16,230 --> 00:14:18,160
and I wanted to see what it was.

238
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:20,160
I'm telling you I didn't do it.

239
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:23,570
If you investigate further, you'll see.

240
00:14:24,370 --> 00:14:26,540
Check where my prints are.

241
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,610
I only touched it lightly with one hand.

242
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:32,480
If I'd really used it as a weapon,
would I have only used one hand?

243
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,910
And this
stock transfer agreement document.

244
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:37,150
We found this on the Chairman's desk.

245
00:14:37,450 --> 00:14:40,080
Since the Chairman's seal isn't on it,

246
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:43,420
- you must've forced him to stamp it.
- What?

247
00:14:43,990 --> 00:14:46,660
I've never seen this document before.

248
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:49,690
We got a report that the two of you
were fighting over company shares.

249
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:54,130
The responding officers testified
that they heard you arguing.

250
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:59,300
That I was arguing with my grandfather?
That never happened.

251
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,140
Chae Hwa Young.

252
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:04,340
Right, Chae Hwa Young set this all up.

253
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:09,110
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

254
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:13,380
It's been days since I felt this free.

255
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:15,590
What about Chairman Ma?

256
00:15:15,590 --> 00:15:17,890
He was in cardiac arrest upon arrival
at the hospital,

257
00:15:17,890 --> 00:15:19,790
but they were able to restart his heart.

258
00:15:20,260 --> 00:15:21,830
He's in emergency surgery now.

259
00:15:21,990 --> 00:15:24,130
That old man just won't die.

260
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:25,900
Why couldn't he just leave this world?

261
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:28,400
What's he hanging on for?

262
00:15:30,170 --> 00:15:33,400
Well then, maybe I should start
playing the part of his daughter...

263
00:15:34,570 --> 00:15:38,040
and tell the board of directors
that I'm Ma Eun Hye.

264
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:44,550
What happened to Oh Jang Mi?

265
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:45,880
You...

266
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:49,290
After you saw with your own eyes
the humiliation I went through,

267
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:50,790
all you can talk about is Oh Jang Mi?

268
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,720
You didn't have to go this far.

269
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:54,990
Why frame Jang Mi for attempted murder?

270
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:57,800
Get her out of there now.
There were plenty of other ways...

271
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,330
to get revenge on Chairman Ma.

272
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,100
Get a grip, Kang Jun Ho!

273
00:16:02,070 --> 00:16:03,300
Did you forget...

274
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,200
Chairman Ma
almost killed Manager Lee and me?

275
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:06,800
Have you forgotten already?

276
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,270
If you want to take over Dream,

277
00:16:08,810 --> 00:16:11,210
don't you dare mention Oh Jang Mi
to me again.

278
00:16:16,050 --> 00:16:17,110
You know what this is, right?

279
00:16:17,780 --> 00:16:19,020
We found it in your bag.

280
00:16:19,380 --> 00:16:20,520
(Rentorix)

281
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,150
What is this?

282
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:25,860
Are you going to keep playing dumb?

283
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:28,890
- It's a powerful diuretic.
- A diuretic?

284
00:16:30,130 --> 00:16:31,330
What's that?

285
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:34,200
I've never seen this medication.

286
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,730
It was in your bag.

287
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:37,400
We also have a tip...

288
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:39,300
that you've been giving it
to Chairman Ma regularly.

289
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:40,340
That's ridiculous.

290
00:16:41,070 --> 00:16:43,170
Why would I give
my grandfather medicine like this?

291
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:45,780
Stop stalling and tell the truth!

292
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,880
Could you stop shouting?

293
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,410
Baek Ho.

294
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:57,420
Oh, dear deities. Please, darling.

295
00:16:57,650 --> 00:16:59,890
(Operating Room)

296
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:03,490
- Suk Hee.
- How's my father?

297
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:04,860
He's okay, right?

298
00:17:04,930 --> 00:17:07,460
(Authorized Personnel Only)

299
00:17:07,530 --> 00:17:08,630
Chae Hwa Young.

300
00:17:08,770 --> 00:17:12,270
Why are you here?
What right do you have to be here?

301
00:17:13,370 --> 00:17:15,910
Did you come to see if he died
because he collapsed?

302
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:20,410
So, you're back to your senses
and running your mouth.

303
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,310
(Surgery in Progress)

304
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:28,150
- My father...
- How is my father?

305
00:17:28,420 --> 00:17:29,520
Is he okay?

306
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:31,860
(Authorized Personnel Only)

307
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,530
The surgery to remove the hematoma
in his brain went well,

308
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:36,390
but the bleeding
was in a very difficult location.

309
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:37,730
He's also elderly.

310
00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:40,430
Plus, his heart function
has been weak for a long time,

311
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,430
so there were several critical moments
during the surgery.

312
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:45,640
So what about now? What's his condition?

313
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:47,270
His cerebral edema could worsen,

314
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:49,810
so I can't say for sure
if he'll regain consciousness.

315
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,340
We'll have to wait and see.

316
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:59,620
Why did Father collapse?

317
00:17:59,950 --> 00:18:01,720
He hasn't been feeling well lately,

318
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:05,390
but he wasn't about
to suddenly collapse like this.

319
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,320
Well...

320
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:11,300
Hey, stop making a scene
and get yourself to the police station.

321
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:13,600
Oh Jang Mi went to the Chairman,

322
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:17,070
shoved a stock agreement in his face,
and tried to kill him.

323
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:19,870
What? That's ridiculous.

324
00:18:19,870 --> 00:18:22,010
And you expect me to believe that?

325
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:24,880
Say that again.
What did you say about Jang Mi?

326
00:18:24,940 --> 00:18:26,410
You think you can just say
whatever you want?

327
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:29,110
Let go. What do you think you're doing?

328
00:18:29,910 --> 00:18:31,550
No, Tae Pyung.

329
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:33,420
Right now, Jang Mi...

330
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:36,490
is being held
for Chairman's attempted murder.

331
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:37,590
What?

332
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:41,490
(Authorized Personnel Only)

333
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:43,330
Jang Mi.

334
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:45,630
Listen to me carefully.

335
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,470
To be honest,

336
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:52,470
the trap Chae Hwa Young set
is very elaborate.

337
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:55,040
To overturn all of this,

338
00:18:56,010 --> 00:18:57,410
it's going to take some time.

339
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:58,910
Then...

340
00:18:59,740 --> 00:19:01,650
am I really going to prison?

341
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,750
It's an attempted murder case,

342
00:19:04,620 --> 00:19:06,650
so a warrant could be issued quickly.

343
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:08,990
You might be sent to a detention center.

344
00:19:09,890 --> 00:19:13,420
But no matter what happens,
I'll get you out as soon as I can,

345
00:19:13,790 --> 00:19:14,860
so don't worry too much.

346
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:16,260
Baek Ho.

347
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,330
I'm so scared.

348
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,270
I'm sorry...

349
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:27,200
I can't get you out of here right away.

350
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,580
This might be a long fight,

351
00:19:32,340 --> 00:19:33,440
but I promise you...

352
00:19:34,410 --> 00:19:36,280
that I will get you out of here
as fast as I can.

353
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,350
Trust me.

354
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:49,530
Where is it?

355
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:51,030
(Detective Division)

356
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:52,600
Baek Ho.

357
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:55,070
Ma'am.

358
00:19:55,870 --> 00:19:57,370
Brace yourself.

359
00:19:58,840 --> 00:20:00,100
What happened, Baek Ho?

360
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:04,140
Jang Mi.

361
00:20:05,940 --> 00:20:09,850
- Mom, why are you here?
- Oh my gosh.

362
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:13,120
- What are we going to do?
- I'm okay.

363
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:16,750
- Baek Ho will help me.
- I can't believe this is happening.

364
00:20:17,090 --> 00:20:18,260
This is unbelievable.

365
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:21,590
You have to stay strong, okay?

366
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:26,130
Baek Ho will do his part,
but I'm going to get you out too.

367
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,870
I won't be helpless
like I was with Seo Rin.

368
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:30,670
I'm not losing my child again.

369
00:20:31,100 --> 00:20:34,240
You know what I mean, right?

370
00:20:38,780 --> 00:20:39,780
Jang Mi.

371
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:44,150
I will be handling Jang Mi's defense.

372
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:46,920
She'll be out soon, so please don't worry.

373
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:50,290
Thank you.

374
00:20:50,990 --> 00:20:52,120
Thank you.

375
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:01,670
The police keep calling.

376
00:21:02,170 --> 00:21:03,500
It's about the witness statement.

377
00:21:04,770 --> 00:21:06,940
Tell them I'm busy
and I'll respond in writing.

378
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,770
The case is attempted patricide,
a serious felony.

379
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:13,140
They'll probably keep pressuring you
to come in as a key witness.

380
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:14,380
I'm sure they will.

381
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:17,880
Still, if I go and they find a weakness,

382
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:19,550
it could backfire on me.

383
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:22,390
By the way,
did you get rid of the speaker?

384
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:25,420
Yes. Team Leader Jin took care of it
right away.

385
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:28,030
Make sure Jin Hong Ju
keeps her mouth shut.

386
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:31,900
Tell her she's finished
if she tells her mom anything about us.

387
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:34,360
Yes, I'm already keeping a close watch
on her.

388
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:37,500
Well then, shall we head home?

389
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:39,300
You fired the housekeeper, right?

390
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:43,940
Hire a couple of good helpers
to clean the place up...

391
00:21:44,170 --> 00:21:46,740
and tell them to prepare a decent meal.

392
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:51,550
I'll call Jun Ho over,
and we'll all start living in that house.

393
00:21:52,820 --> 00:21:54,850
Yes. Understood.

394
00:21:56,050 --> 00:21:57,750
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

395
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:02,890
Hwa Young.

396
00:22:02,890 --> 00:22:06,060
I couldn't reach you all this time.
I was worried.

397
00:22:07,260 --> 00:22:08,900
I had some things to take care of.

398
00:22:09,630 --> 00:22:12,900
Nam Bong, our dream has come true.

399
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,940
What?

400
00:22:13,940 --> 00:22:18,740
You, me, and Jun Ho can live together now.

401
00:22:19,410 --> 00:22:21,380
Is that really true?

402
00:22:22,050 --> 00:22:25,250
Nam Bong, you're staying
at your studio apartment now, right?

403
00:22:25,750 --> 00:22:29,150
Give it back to Han Young Ja
and come to my house.

404
00:22:29,150 --> 00:22:30,250
Right now.

405
00:22:31,390 --> 00:22:35,460
I'll make a delicious dinner
and wait for you.

406
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:37,130
You mean right now?

407
00:22:37,130 --> 00:22:39,660
Okay. I love you, Hwa Young.

408
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:42,300
It feels like a dream.

409
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:50,240
It's been so long
since I last felt this happy and free.

410
00:22:51,370 --> 00:22:53,610
To think the three of us
are finally going to live together.

411
00:22:57,950 --> 00:22:59,020
Chae Hwa Young.

412
00:23:00,580 --> 00:23:04,050
- What did you do to my Jang Mi?
- Let go of me.

413
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:05,320
You want to end up
at the police station too?

414
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:06,960
I'm warning you.

415
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:10,490
If anything happens
to my father or Jang Mi,

416
00:23:10,490 --> 00:23:12,600
I'll kill you and go to prison.

417
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:14,260
Let go. You're hurting me.

418
00:23:14,330 --> 00:23:17,470
You think I won't do it?
Get Jang Mi out of there now.

419
00:23:17,500 --> 00:23:21,870
- If you don't, I won't stay still.
- Do you have any proof I did it?

420
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:25,440
Show me the proof you love so much.
Now let go.

421
00:23:26,810 --> 00:23:28,380
You think I can't do it?

422
00:23:28,610 --> 00:23:31,850
I already died once 30 years ago.

423
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:35,020
I can just kill you and then die myself.

424
00:23:35,620 --> 00:23:37,150
You'd better be ready, Chae Hwa Young.

425
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:40,760
You could just die out of nowhere
while walking down the street.

426
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:56,970
The forensics team already finished up.

427
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:58,640
Yes, just in case.

428
00:23:59,910 --> 00:24:03,550
Mrs. Yang, you can't work here anymore?

429
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:06,020
They told me to quit, so I have to go.
What else can I do?

430
00:24:06,250 --> 00:24:10,020
The Chairman will wake up soon,
and Jang Mi will be back.

431
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:12,160
You'll be able to see them again soon.

432
00:24:12,990 --> 00:24:14,590
Thank you for everything, Mrs. Yang.

433
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:17,630
I'm leaving without even getting
to say thank you to them for everything.

434
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:20,030
Lawyer Kang, please tell them for me.

435
00:24:20,430 --> 00:24:21,430
I will.

436
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:30,340
Go to Chairman Ma's study
and find the evidence.

437
00:24:34,180 --> 00:24:35,880
It must have been open
during the accident.

438
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:49,090
(Asset Management,
Voting Rights Entrustment)

439
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:52,760
"I, Choi Myung Chul, until my grandson,
Choi Ha Joon, comes of age..."

440
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:54,900
"and can exercise his own rights,"

441
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:58,000
"entrust all voting and property rights
for all shares..."

442
00:24:58,270 --> 00:25:01,610
"fully to Ma Dae Chang,
and hereby notarize this."

443
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:09,180
(Power of Attorney,
Shareholder: Choi Ha Joon)

444
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:11,380
(Shareholder: Choi Ha Joon,
Guardian: Choi Myung Chul)

445
00:25:11,380 --> 00:25:13,380
(Agent Proxy: Ma Dae Chang)

446
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:26,260
(Choi Myung Chul)

447
00:25:26,360 --> 00:25:27,360
This is...

448
00:25:27,930 --> 00:25:31,270
Why does the Chairman
have my grandfather's official seal?

449
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:35,740
And he's been posing as my proxy
this whole time.

450
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:48,790
Dad,

451
00:25:49,490 --> 00:25:50,820
you have to be strong.

452
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:55,230
Be strong and come back to me.

453
00:25:55,890 --> 00:25:58,060
I came back to you.

454
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:02,330
It's me, your daughter, Eun Hye.

455
00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:04,800
I'll never break down.

456
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:08,240
So don't worry, and just be strong.

457
00:26:09,340 --> 00:26:10,440
Dad.

458
00:26:19,150 --> 00:26:20,150
Chae Hwa Young.

459
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,290
You can laugh all you want for now...

460
00:26:23,150 --> 00:26:26,760
because it won't be long
until you're crying tears of blood.

461
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:36,870
It feels like a dream...

462
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:39,300
having a nice, quiet family meal at home.

463
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,370
Don't you think so, Jun Ho?

464
00:26:42,310 --> 00:26:44,470
- Nam Bong.
- I couldn't...

465
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,240
believe my ears earlier.

466
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:49,410
I only ever dreamed of this.

467
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:52,420
I never imagined
it would actually become reality.

468
00:26:53,180 --> 00:26:57,890
I know.
Let's toast to our family's happy future.

469
00:26:58,360 --> 00:27:01,320
To celebrate our family becoming one,

470
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:03,490
let's have a grand toast.

471
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:07,760
The great writer Goethe
once famously said,

472
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:12,040
"Love is the crown of life."

473
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:16,070
The reason my life has felt so empty
until now...

474
00:27:16,370 --> 00:27:20,540
was that it lacked
the dazzling crown, Chae Hwa Young.

475
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:24,910
Now with you and our Jun Ho here,

476
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:28,790
my life's crown is finally complete.

477
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:34,190
So, here's to our family's glorious love.

478
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:47,470
What are you doing here?

479
00:27:48,610 --> 00:27:50,610
Manager Lee,
what do you think you're doing?

480
00:27:50,670 --> 00:27:52,710
How dare you interrupt us
at a time like this?

481
00:27:53,110 --> 00:27:55,050
Manager Lee, what are you doing?

482
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:58,880
A family that was torn apart
is finally reuniting.

483
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,550
On such a moving occasion,

484
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:07,260
The son’s real father can’t be left out,
can he?

485
00:28:08,730 --> 00:28:09,730
What?

486
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,830
Real father?

487
00:28:12,430 --> 00:28:14,100
Lee Kang Hyuk, you...

488
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:15,370
Lee Kang Hyuk is Jun Ho's...

489
00:28:17,130 --> 00:28:18,330
He's your father?

490
00:28:58,740 --> 00:29:00,180
(The First Man)

491
00:29:00,280 --> 00:29:02,080
Chae Hwa Young
has probably gotten to the detectives...

492
00:29:02,150 --> 00:29:03,380
and the Prosecutor's Office by now.

493
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,010
You don't have a choice.

494
00:29:05,010 --> 00:29:07,450
I'm not here to negotiate.
I'm here to tell you how it's going to be.

495
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:11,350
Once this shareholders' meeting is over,
Dream will officially be mine.

496
00:29:11,420 --> 00:29:13,590
Isn't this more than enough
for lobbying funds?

497
00:29:13,660 --> 00:29:15,960
No, we have to make it airtight.

498
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:18,700
How much longer are we going to let
that wretched woman get away with this?

499
00:29:18,700 --> 00:29:21,970
Let's bleed her dry so she has
nothing left to bribe people with.

500
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:25,170
Chae Hwa Young, your kingdom ends here.

501
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:29,210
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
